        {
            "title": "OpenAI聲稱DeepSeek蒸餾美國AI模型以獲取優勢",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"OpenAI聲稱DeepSeek蒸餾美國AI模型以獲取優勢\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/iYVpkn6YlV4TVpmggxlzCA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2025-12/bcc597d0-d16a-11f0-976f-d07af68cd8ab\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">OpenAI聲稱DeepSeek蒸餾美國AI模型以獲取優勢</figcaption></div></figure></div>",
